他…为什么要怀疑我？

237
00:15:10,74 --> 00:15:13,04
At first,he thought it was Joseph...
因为原先他以为是乔瑟…

238
00:15:13,27 --> 00:15:16,80
...but after he asked Joseph about it, turns out it was you.
…但在问了乔瑟之后 发现结果是你

239
00:15:18,88 --> 00:15:22,32
-Anyway,I thought you should know. -All right. That's it.
反正我想你应该知道啦 好吧，够了

240
00:15:22,55 --> 00:15:23,81
Look,Joey...
听我说，乔伊…

241
00:15:24,05 --> 00:15:26,92
... I realize this is the role of a lifetime for you...
…对不起，我了解这是你 这辈子最重要的一个角色…

242
00:15:27,12 --> 00:15:31,29
...and if I could just fire Joseph, I would. But that's not possible.
…若我可以只开除乔瑟就好了 不幸的是，那是不可能的

243
00:15:31,49 --> 00:15:33,22
So I have to let you both go.
所以我必须要开除你们两个

244
00:15:35,30 --> 00:15:37,32
What? Everybody loves Joseph.
你在胡扯什么？大家都爱乔瑟

245
00:15:37,56 --> 00:15:39,56
I don't. I hate Joseph.
我不爱，我恨乔瑟

246
00:15:40,94 --> 00:15:43,06
I think he's a brown-nosing suck-up.
我认为他是个马屁精

247
00:15:45,57 --> 00:15:48,84
You can't fire Joseph. He's not in your department.
是吗？你不能开除他 因为他不在你的部门

248
00:15:53,95 --> 00:15:57,25
All right,okay. So I can't fire Joseph...
好吧…我不能开除他…

249
00:15:57,82 --> 00:15:59,51
... but I can sleep with his wife.
…但是我可以跟他老婆睡

250
00:16:02,99 --> 00:16:03,85
Not Karen!
凯伦，不！

251
00:16:04,16 --> 00:16:07,46
Yeah,I'm thinking about having an affair with her.
我正在考虑跟她搞婚外情

252
00:16:07,66 --> 00:16:08,86
You know what?
你知道吗？

253
00:16:09,70 --> 00:16:10,53
I just did.
刚搞了

254
00:16:14,13 --> 00:16:15,90
What the hell are you doing?
你对我做了什么，老兄？

255
00:16:16,10 --> 00:16:17,37
Oh,it's not me.
不是我

256
00:16:17,60 --> 00:16:18,94
It's my character!
是我的角色

257
00:16:19,87 --> 00:16:20,70
Chandie.
钱迪

258
00:16:22,21 --> 00:16:25,51
The rogue processor who seduces his coworkers' wives...
对，为了好玩 而引诱同事老婆的坏处理员…

259
00:16:25,71 --> 00:16:27,68
...and then laughs about it.
…隔天在饮水机旁边当笑话讲

260
00:16:27,95 --> 00:16:31,38
In fact,I have her panties right there in my drawer!
其实她的内裤就在我的抽屉里

261
00:16:31,62 --> 00:16:34,11
-Really? -No,freak show,she's fictional!
真的吗？ 假的，疯子，根本没有这个人

262
00:16:35,69 --> 00:16:36,78
Take it easy.
放轻松一点

263
00:16:37,29 --> 00:16:41,69
If it means that much to you, I'll go find something else.
这对你那么重要的话 那我找别的事做好了

264
00:16:42,70 --> 00:16:43,99
Thank you.
谢谢你

265
00:16:45,87 --> 00:16:49,32
It's just that I'm gonna miss Joseph.
只是我会想念乔瑟的

266
00:16:50,04 --> 00:16:52,23
I liked him. His wife.
我喜欢他，和他太太

267
00:16:52,54 --> 00:16:53,80
She was hot.
她好火辣

268
00:16:58,81 --> 00:17:01,41
Please take these off. I swear I won't scratch.
拜托你拆掉，我发誓我不抓了

269
00:17:01,72 --> 00:17:03,88
No,sorry,hon. Monica's orders.
对不起，摩妮卡的命令

270
00:17:05,85 --> 00:17:07,88
Well,that wasn't easy.
真不简单

271
00:17:09,32 --> 00:17:10,92
Okay,dinner's on.
晚餐好了

272
00:17:11,89 --> 00:17:14,16
There's a peach cobbler warming in the oven.
烤箱里还有一个桃子饼在保温

273
00:17:14,36 --> 00:17:18,49
So the plate's gonna be hot,but that shouldn't be a problem for you.
盘子会很烫手 但那应该不成问题才对

274
00:17:20,23 --> 00:17:22,07
All right,you kids. Bye,now.
好了，孩子们，拜拜

275
00:17:22,34 --> 00:17:24,17
-Bye. -Oh,look,look.
拜拜 你们看

276
00:17:24,37 --> 00:17:26,20
A low-budget puppet show.
低成本的木偶剧

277
00:17:28,38 --> 00:17:31,44
A shame you can't see what finger I'm holding up.
真可惜你看不到 我举起的是哪一根手指

278
00:17:35,88 --> 00:17:37,75
-Wine? -Please.
酒？ 麻烦你

279
00:17:47,90 --> 00:17:50,23
-Spilled some. -I got it.
泼出来了 我来

280
00:18:01,98 --> 00:18:03,91
