你说什么？

282
00:18:07,48 --> 00:18:08,38
Sorry.
对不起

283
00:18:11,62 --> 00:18:12,64
You look beautiful.
你好美

284
00:18:29,80 --> 00:18:32,14
You know what? That's it. That's it.
够了，我受够了

285
00:18:40,18 --> 00:18:41,01
Oh,yes.
真好

286
00:18:43,48 --> 00:18:44,31
Good.
好

287
00:18:50,09 --> 00:18:51,42
You guys,did you?
你们…

288
00:19:01,30 --> 00:19:02,13
Monica...
摩妮卡…

289
00:19:02,37 --> 00:19:03,46
...wake up.
…醒醒

290
00:19:04,77 --> 00:19:06,00
What's up?
什么事？

291
00:19:06,21 --> 00:19:07,54
I thought of a thing.
我想到一个了

292
00:19:11,91 --> 00:19:12,84
Yeah?
是吗？

293
00:19:14,52 --> 00:19:18,68
I have to sleep,have to, on this side of the bed.
对，我必须睡…我必须… 睡床的这一边

294
00:19:20,69 --> 00:19:23,68
No. You have to sleep on this side of the bed...
你必须睡床的这一边…

295
00:19:23,96 --> 00:19:26,86
... because I have to sleep on this side of the bed.
…是因为我必须睡床的这一边

296
00:19:28,80 --> 00:19:31,46
Or so I would have you believe.
还是因为我让你那么相信

297
00:19:34,67 --> 00:19:38,50
So you have a side of the bed. Everybody has a side of the bed.
没什么大不了啊 这毛病大家都有

298
00:19:38,74 --> 00:19:41,64
Hey,come on. You haven't heard my reason yet.
别这样嘛 你还没听我的理由呢

299
00:19:42,04 --> 00:19:43,74
All right,go on.
好啊，说吧

300
00:19:45,15 --> 00:19:47,41
I have to sleep on the west side...
我必须睡在床的西边…

301
00:19:47,65 --> 00:19:50,74
... because I grew up in California...
…因为我是在加州长大的…

302
00:19:50,98 --> 00:19:52,58
...and otherwise...
…睡东边的话…

303
00:19:53,09 --> 00:19:56,21
...the ocean would be on the wrong side.
…海洋的方向就错了

304
00:20:01,20 --> 00:20:02,53
Oh,my God.
天啊

305
00:20:02,73 --> 00:20:04,59
You're a freak!
你真变态

306
00:20:05,67 --> 00:20:07,07
How about that?
你觉得怎么样？

307
00:20:11,57 --> 00:20:13,10
Where're you shipping off to?
莱恩，你这次要潜到哪里？

308
00:20:13,44 --> 00:20:14,60
I really can't say.
我真的不能说

309
00:20:14,84 --> 00:20:17,07
Do you have nuclear weapons onboard?
那你们潜水艇上有核武吗？

310
00:20:17,78 --> 00:20:18,90
I can't say.
我不能说

311
00:20:19,21 --> 00:20:22,01
Do you get to look through a periscope thingy?
那你是不是可以用 潜水望眼镜那种东西看东西？

312
00:20:22,22 --> 00:20:24,08
I'm sorry,but I can't say.
对不起，我不能说

313
00:20:24,28 --> 00:20:27,19
Wow,it's neat learning about submarines.
学潜水艇的知识真酷

314
00:20:27,96 --> 00:20:30,79
-I better not miss my flight. -I'll walk you out.
该走了不然会错过飞机 我送你出去

315
00:20:31,02 --> 00:20:33,42
-Bye,Ryan. -Pleasure. Take care.
拜拜，莱恩 幸会了

316
00:20:39,10 --> 00:20:43,54
So do you think we could get you one of those uniform things?
你想我们可以 弄套制服给你穿吗？

317
00:20:44,87 --> 00:20:46,46
You like that,do you?
你喜欢，是不是？

318
00:20:46,74 --> 00:20:47,97
Oh,yeah.
是呀

319
00:20:48,21 --> 00:20:49,57
I'll make some calls.
我去打电话

320
00:20:52,08 --> 00:20:54,55
Can you believe that's how we spent our two weeks?
你相信我们两个礼拜 是这样共度的吗？

321
00:20:54,75 --> 00:20:56,58
We didn't do the romantic things I'd planned...
我知道，我计划的浪漫事 我们没一件事做过…

322
00:20:56,78 --> 00:21:01,41
...Iike having a picnic in Central Park and coffee at Central Perk.
…像去中央公园野餐 还有来中央公园喝咖啡

323
00:21:01,62 --> 00:21:03,11
Oh,I just got that!
我们刚喝过了

324
00:21:12,47 --> 00:21:13,80
Taxi!
计程车

325
00:21:19,91 --> 00:21:20,93
Bye,you.
再见

326
00:21:34,42 --> 00:21:35,85
I'm sorry,we're
对不起，我们打烊…

327
00:21:39,36 --> 00:21:40,55
Hey,sailor.
水手

328
00:21:40,76 --> 00:21:42,39
Is this what you had in mind?
这是你心里想的吗？

329
00:21:43,96 --> 00:21:44,79
I'll say.
可不是

330
00:21:50,87 --> 00:21:52,86
I'm shipping out tomorrow.
我明天就要出海了

331
00:21:53,41 --> 00:21:54,74
Well,then...
那么…

332
00:21:56,98 --> 00:21:58,95
...we better make this night count.
…春宵别虚度了

333
00:22:01,32 --> 00:22:04,15
Wait,I forgot to turn off the cappuccino machine.
等等，我忘了关咖啡机了

334
00:22:12,89 --> 00:22:14,62
Anchors aweigh.
起锚吧

335
00:22:16,83 --> 00:22:19,46
Oh,wait,wait! My purse,my purse!
等等… 我的皮包

336
00:22:25,31 --> 00:22:27,90
I forgot to turn off the bathroom light.
我忘了关洗手间的灯

337
00:22:28,11 --> 00:22:30,17
Why don't I just meet you upstairs?
我们干脆楼上见好了

338
00:22:35,18 --> 00:22:36,11
Honey!
蜜糖

